      <extensionElements>
         <signavio:signavioDiagramMetaData metaKey="meta-processdescription" metaValue="Customer Planning &amp; shipping schedule refers to a prearranged or predetermined time and conditions under which a particular item or shipment is expected to be delivered to a customer. Planning and scheduling play a pivotal role in customer satisfaction and overall business success. Planning and scheduling can be improved by leveraging SAP best practices resulting in efficient supply chain operations"/>
